{"tid":930590,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet親自指認「最不愛洗澡的成員」！當事人「超委屈」","createTime":"2018-12-06T12:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T14:32:09.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b45eb71bcccf3ce1338cf659228b3cc1bf9bb5de","tid":930590,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"Red Velvet親自指認「最不愛洗澡的成員」！當事人「超委屈」可愛反應引發全場大笑！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2018/12/06/550_1368787_1544068179.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2F550_1368787_1544068179.webp&h=afadd169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5日，《演藝家中介》節目組公開Red Velvet游擊約會的未播出影像，在「指名TALK時間」的環節中，主持人問到：「一起經歷了超過5年以上的宿舍生活，彼此之間應該沒有什麼是不知道的吧？現在請指出最不愛洗澡的成員！」一開始大家以為五票都是投給Wendy，沒想到...<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2018/12/06/550_1368790_1544068187.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2F550_1368790_1544068187.webp&h=e8fa747b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJoy卻說：「瑟琪歐逆！」Irene也跟著說：「我也是瑟琪！」Wendy聽完感到超驚喜立刻大喊：「那我也要改！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/530/2018/12/06/530_1368766_1544067847.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F530%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2F530_1368766_1544067847.webp&h=5eb8662f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/530/2018/12/06/530_1368769_1544067943.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F530%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2F530_1368769_1544067943.webp&h=be4598c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最後還是抗爭失敗，被判定為Red Velvet之中最不愛洗澡的成員<br />\n瑟琪解釋：「我是在大家都睡著之後才去洗澡的，所以她們才會沒有看到！」可愛的語氣引發眾人大笑<br />\n瑟琪還補充：「我現在甚至還會連乳液都擦完才去就寢！」一旁的Wendy聽了之後表示：「乳液沒有吧？」瑟琪回說：「我承認以前真的沒有，但是最近想法已經改變了~」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3W9qiqWW02M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3W9qiqWW02M&d=emraIeL7nabu%2FhUr1ikBlC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5f1f0ec1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3W9qiqWW02M</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/5YeeepKG019DYyRWEP/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F5YeeepKG019DYyRWEP%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8b783984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1712/ej131571696413664042357.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1712%2Fej131571696413664042357.gif&h=58517d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1712/ej1315716964309643084898.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1712%2Fej1315716964309643084898.gif&h=1640740e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解可以咁可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279bbd1d07723ec31149c89c086c05c5689be9b6","tid":930590,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"美極<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb42b49b323c71591d050a277cb15c0fde56232","tid":930590,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"隻雞臭架！！"},{"pid":"696a6cddecfa1714ed68bb83e97dddf2d57dc213","tid":930590,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"佢都係我屋企洗"},{"pid":"fa80c5892f1ea2a8a869b735025d5b9a069b7bf1","tid":930590,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201